---
  <section id="testimonials">
    <div class="section-header" style="text-align:left">
      <span class="label" style="color:var(--gray-orange)">Client Stories</span>
      <h2 style="color:var(--dark-brown)">What Our Guests <em>Remember</em></h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testi-card">
        <p class="testi-quote">"Elamrit transformed our daughter's wedding into a culinary spectacle. Every dish told a
          story — from the welcome sharbat to the final dessert. Our guests are still talking about it months later."
        </p>
        <div class="testi-divider"></div>
        <div class="testi-name">Priya &amp; Anand Kulkarni</div>
        <div class="testi-event">Wedding · Pune · 400 Guests</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card">
        <p class="testi-quote">"For our annual leadership conference, we needed catering that matched our brand's
          premium positioning. Elamrit delivered flawlessly — the live stations were a talking point for days."</p>
        <div class="testi-divider"></div>
        <div class="testi-name">Rohan Mehta</div>
        <div class="testi-event">Corporate Gala · Mumbai · 250 Guests</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card">
        <p class="testi-quote">"The private dining experience they curated for our anniversary was breathtaking. A
          7-course menu designed around our story. I've never felt more celebrated."</p>
        <div class="testi-divider"></div>
        <div class="testi-name">Seema Nair</div>
        <div class="testi-event">Private Dining · Pune · Intimate</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
